It was pretty goddamn silly. I actually laughed out loud while it was happening, probably annoying some other people in the crowd, but I couldn't help it. That said, of the group I went with, several of them said it just wouldn't have been right without it and that it was a fantastic callback. Also, I liked the way they reversed the Spock and Kirk scene from TWOK there. It was one of the things that finally broke through Spock's peronal barriers and Spock chasing after and fighting with Khan was pretty great.
